        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 2. — A-C, Choanostomellia filatovae (Zenkevitch, 1964); A, ventral view of anterior part of female; B, gonoduct; C, right anal vesicle; D-F, Torbenwolffia galatheae Zenkevitch, 1966; D, ventral view of anterior part of female; E, gonoduct; F, left anal vesicle. Abbreviations: av, anal vesicle; co, collar; gd, gonoduct; gp, genital pore; gs, gonostome; nc, nerve cord; pr, proboscis. Scale bars: A, 5 mm; B, 2 mm; C, E, F, 1 mm; D, 4 mm." ;
